{"tid":1534902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Zara發聲明強調非響應罷工 支持一國兩制　","createTime":"2019-09-03T07:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T04:20:37.000Z","uid":31324,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"033aca2d332bb97b068fab3990d06aa69f926add","tid":1534902,"uid":31324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:07:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1082567/即時-香港-Zara發聲明強調非響應罷工-支持一國兩制\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1082567%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-Zara%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E9%9D%9E%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFB3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=fcded4fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1082567%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-Zara%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E%E5%BC%B7%E8%AA%BF%E9%9D%9E%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E4%B8%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A9%E5%88%B6&h=d9a01997\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1082567/即時-香港-Zara發聲明強調非響應罷工-支持一國兩制</a><br />\n<br />\n連鎖服裝品牌Zara昨日在網民應三罷「罷工」、「罷課」及「罷市」期間，港九多間分店暫停營業，門外貼出的告示未有解釋原因，被內地傳媒質疑是響應罷工。Zara昨日深夜在官方微博發表聲明，指擁護中華人民共和國領土主權完整，一貫支持一國兩制。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指出，公司從未支持罷工，亦未有發布相關言論或進行相關行為。<br />\n<br />\n似乎轉頭又清算員工<br />\n罷買 Zara <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9dd348c7a4cede589c1b61d5ff7b7cd7edc00b","tid":1534902,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:07:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f48acc4fdf1a75aabbeacbea2d0db6ae4c98fa71","tid":1534902,"uid":78570,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"人地果日都罷左市啦"},{"pid":"fe17c68d454aadcb7650e32e4fdabc1a89155d82","tid":1534902,"uid":80228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:02:09.000Z","msg":"公司逼9同事衝番去開舖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23af1325fc6a20b916991792c9bf2e6c3cf61aac","tid":1534902,"uid":319555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:20:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>有無其他Inditex bands有嘢講有嘢爆？歡迎爆料或留tg俾我</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n入呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全世界入］Zara正仆街 唔撚理員工安全<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1555932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1555932</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}